Package: rpolecat
Type: Package
Title: Download and Transform the POLECAT Event Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Andreas", family = "Beger", role = c("cre", "aut"),
           email = "andy@basilanalytics.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1883-3169")),
    person(given = "Benjamin E.", family = "Bagozzi", role = c("aut"),
           email = "bagozzib@udel.edu")
    )
Maintainer: Andreas Beger <andy@basilanalytics.com>
Description: Download, manage, and analyze the POLECAT political event data
    from Harvard Dataverse. Provides functions for downloading and updating
    local data, filtering and aggregating events, mapping events to quad
    categories, database storage via DuckDB or SQLite, country code
    translation, and geocoding events to GADM administrative units.
